            "body": "Thank you for the explanation. \r\n\r\n> The last number in the semver is a monotonic timestamp, not a hash.\r\n\r\nThat's interesting, I failed to make that connection. I apologize if that is documented somewhere.\r\n\r\n> DESTDIR must be an absolute path, use $PWD and not a dot.\r\n\r\nYes, I realized my mistake after posting this; of course the build works then.\r\n",
